---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 156
By: Sri Ramakrishna
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Renunciation-Detachment=Interiorization and Transmutation
    of the Faculties
  - 64
---
God cannot be seen so long as there is the slightest taint of desire;
therefore have thy small desires satisfied, and renounce the big desires by
right reasoning and discrimination.
